{"tid":2248741,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Xianggang政府:將修訂國旗及國徽條例  以配合人大常委會對國旗法國徽法的修訂","createTime":"2020-10-18T23:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T23:33:54.000Z","uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cedb1a415c10ed80d3542e70614bbd5ce1326191","tid":2248741,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T23:25:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第13屆全國人民代表大會常務委員會第22次會議今日正式通過《中華人民共和國國旗法（修正草案）》及《中華人民共和國國徽法（修正草案）》。特區政府表示會對《國旗及國徽條例》作出適當修訂，以實施適用於香港特區的規定，履行憲制責任。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《國旗法》及《國徽法》1997年7月1日納入《基本法》附件三，並透過制定《國旗及國徽條例》以本地立法方式在香港特區實施。</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/10/20201017/20201017_212817_452.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2020%2F10%2F20201017%2F20201017_212817_452.html&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=d6dc8b53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/10/20201017/20201017_212817_452.html</a>"},{"pid":"0775e09224b69ab245ee9e5a99a8548f6efd9f84","tid":2248741,"uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T23:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>内地傳媒報道，修改後的國旗法、國徽法，進一步禁止損害國旗和國徽尊嚴的行為。其中國旗法規定，不得倒掛、倒插或以其他有損國旗尊嚴的方式升掛和使用國旗，亦不得隨意丟棄國旗。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">修改後的法律規定，在公共場合故意以焚燒、毀損、塗劃、玷污、踐踏等方式侮辱國旗、國徽，依法追究刑事責任，情節較輕則由公安機關處以15日以下拘留。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n另外，法律亦增加國旗、國徽的適用場合，例如規定中央政府駐香港、澳門有關機構，應當在工作日升掛國旗並懸掛國徽。</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555283-20201017.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555283-20201017.htm&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=4f5a86a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555283-20201017.htm&h=562bc068\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555283-20201017.htm</a>"},{"pid":"962bc52a566408d52fbc7cec82bfdeda803223a4","tid":2248741,"uid":230530,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T23:28:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/KOQUTRLD35A4JPLNKX7SPDRLBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FKOQUTRLD35A4JPLNKX7SPDRLBA%2F&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=4d33aae5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200813%2FKOQUTRLD35A4JPLNKX7SPDRLBA%2F&h=42ea0f54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200813/KOQUTRLD35A4JPLNKX7SPDRLBA/</a> <br />\n九龍城警署疑扯錯旗 區旗涉違例大過國旗 國旗陳舊褪色<br />\n<br />\n支持炎症執法！.！"},{"pid":"1082099ffe0df6d0fc036e14637d0a8b7c2ef5b2","tid":2248741,"uid":131792,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T23:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kvSTxhO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkvSTxhO.gif&h=948232c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wXCt4Mq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwXCt4Mq.png&h=d3315232&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0485e346dccd0bf720761351f9ab230c3e453fd","tid":2248741,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1082099ffe0df6d0fc036e14637d0a8b7c2ef5b2","tid":2248741,"uid":131792,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T23:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kvSTxhO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkvSTxhO.gif&h=948232c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wXCt4Mq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwXCt4Mq.png&h=d3315232&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T23:32:41.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig